        HttpStatus getStatusCode()
        Return the HTTP status code of the response.
        返回:
        the HTTP status as an HttpStatus enum value
        抛出:
        IllegalArgumentException - in case of an unknown HTTP status code
        另请参阅:
        HttpStatus.valueOf(int)
